1
00:00:36,700 --> 00:00:42,060
=Twin Fire Dawn=

2
00:00:42,100 --> 00:00:45,060
=Episode 24=

3
00:00:45,620 --> 00:00:46,580
Xue Wan,

4
00:00:47,000 --> 00:00:48,720
whatever grievance you have,
take it out on me.

5
00:00:54,140 --> 00:00:57,460
Please, don't make things difficult
for her anymore.

6
00:00:59,340 --> 00:01:00,420
Nianchi.

7
00:01:01,580 --> 00:01:03,220
You've been deceived by her.

8
00:01:04,180 --> 00:01:05,220
You'll regret this.

9
00:01:06,220 --> 00:01:06,980
Xue Wan.

10
00:01:08,060 --> 00:01:08,820
Xue Wan.

11
00:01:11,020 --> 00:01:11,820
Commander,

12
00:01:12,340 --> 00:01:13,140
I'll go after her.

13
00:01:18,740 --> 00:01:19,660
Shaoyuan.

14
00:01:21,140 --> 00:01:22,660
I can't leave you.

15
00:01:23,180 --> 00:01:25,460
But I truly feel sorry for her.

16
00:01:25,980 --> 00:01:27,140
What should I do?

17
00:01:28,260 --> 00:01:29,460
This isn't your fault.

18
00:01:31,680 --> 00:01:33,540
The man she was supposed
to marry wasn't me either.

19
00:01:35,180 --> 00:01:36,220
Maybe

20
00:01:37,300 --> 00:01:38,900
this was fate's arrangement all along.

21
00:02:24,780 --> 00:02:26,060
How could you be so careless?

22
00:02:30,540 --> 00:02:31,940
I'm telling you,

23
00:02:32,100 --> 00:02:34,620
my heart has been feeling uneasy
these past two days.

24
00:02:36,900 --> 00:02:37,740
You,

25
00:02:38,420 --> 00:02:39,860
you're always overthinking things.

26
00:02:40,980 --> 00:02:42,060
I think

27
00:02:42,100 --> 00:02:45,460
you should just spend more time admiring
your beautiful flower room every day.

28
00:02:46,140 --> 00:02:47,580
You'll feel much better.

29
00:02:50,220 --> 00:02:51,140
Alright.

30
00:02:53,660 --> 00:02:54,300
Report.

31
00:02:54,500 --> 00:02:57,020
A female corpse has been discovered
behind the Commander's Residence.

32
00:02:57,780 --> 00:02:58,340
What?

33
00:02:59,760 --> 00:03:00,620
Alright, I understand.

34
00:03:01,660 --> 00:03:03,180
Darling, I'll go take a look.

35
00:03:03,260 --> 00:03:04,100
Wait.

36
00:03:08,100 --> 00:03:09,700
This is the jade pendant you gave me.

37
00:03:09,980 --> 00:03:11,260
It once blocked a bullet for me.

38
00:03:11,900 --> 00:03:13,260
I've had it repaired.

39
00:03:13,300 --> 00:03:14,660
You should wear it with you.

40
00:03:15,180 --> 00:03:16,820
May it keep you safe and sound too.

41
00:03:22,140 --> 00:03:23,300
My Darling,

42
00:03:24,140 --> 00:03:25,660
I'm only going to the back courtyard.

43
00:03:26,580 --> 00:03:27,380
Don't worry.

44
00:03:32,260 --> 00:03:32,900
Go on then.

45
00:04:05,380 --> 00:04:06,140
Commander,

46
00:04:06,940 --> 00:04:09,540
Xinran's estimated time of death
was around two days ago.

47
00:04:09,780 --> 00:04:12,900
And it appears she suffered abuse
before her death.

48
00:04:17,600 --> 00:04:18,920
Have you found anyone suspicious?

49
00:04:19,100 --> 00:04:22,020
To avoid alerting the enemy,
I've already had people quietly investigate.

50
00:04:22,540 --> 00:04:25,180
But no suspicious individuals
have been found.

51
00:04:26,180 --> 00:04:27,660
Who would dare

52
00:04:29,580 --> 00:04:31,620
commit murder right under my nose?

53
00:04:40,260 --> 00:04:41,420
Shaoyuan.

54
00:04:42,180 --> 00:04:43,580
Didn't you just go out?

55
00:05:07,540 --> 00:05:08,779
Tell them to be extra careful.

56
00:05:08,780 --> 00:05:09,620
Alright.

57
00:05:14,180 --> 00:05:14,940
Yi?

58
00:05:24,100 --> 00:05:25,540
It's me, Yunqiu.

59
00:05:26,020 --> 00:05:28,900
Cheng Yi, why are you here?

60
00:05:30,620 --> 00:05:32,980
Why do you have
so many fresh knife wounds on you?

61
00:05:34,740 --> 00:05:37,700
Yunqiu,

62
00:05:38,780 --> 00:05:40,420
are you that interested in my body?

63
00:05:42,500 --> 00:05:43,660
These knife wounds...

64
00:05:45,220 --> 00:05:46,860
Do they look familiar to you?

65
00:05:51,620 --> 00:05:52,900
Answer me.

66
00:06:03,340 --> 00:06:05,700
(Land Ownership Certificate)

67
00:06:06,620 --> 00:06:07,660
Thank you, Commander.

68
00:06:09,140 --> 00:06:10,620
Why call me Commander all of a sudden?

69
00:06:14,700 --> 00:06:15,580
You...

70
00:06:16,300 --> 00:06:19,380
Since when did you start
putting sugar in your coffee?

71
00:06:21,220 --> 00:06:23,740
Just felt like
trying something different.

72
00:06:30,500 --> 00:06:31,820
Could it really be him?

73
00:06:34,180 --> 00:06:35,020
Yunqiu.

74
00:06:38,540 --> 00:06:39,540
Yunqiu!

75
00:06:41,140 --> 00:06:42,100
Yunqiu!

76
00:06:45,460 --> 00:06:46,420
Yunqiu!

77
00:06:49,620 --> 00:06:50,580
Yunqiu!

78
00:06:55,220 --> 00:06:56,100
Yunqiu!

79
00:06:59,980 --> 00:07:00,900
Yunqiu!

80
00:07:01,140 --> 00:07:02,060
Shaoyuan.

81
00:07:10,820 --> 00:07:12,180
Gu Shaoyan.

82
00:07:12,980 --> 00:07:15,140
Looks like nothing can escape your eyes.

83
00:07:15,700 --> 00:07:17,780
Was my disguise really that poor?

84
00:07:18,260 --> 00:07:19,180
Where's Yunqiu?

85
00:07:20,300 --> 00:07:21,260
This way, please.

86
00:07:36,660 --> 00:07:37,380
Gu Shaoyan.

87
00:07:41,380 --> 00:07:43,540
I already told you,
my name isn't Gu Shaoyan.

88
00:07:43,980 --> 00:07:45,580
I'm Cheng Yi now.

89
00:07:46,140 --> 00:07:47,420
Cheng Yi.

90
00:07:47,460 --> 00:07:48,780
Do you understand?

91
00:07:49,660 --> 00:07:50,540
Where's Yunqiu?

92
00:07:51,980 --> 00:07:53,340
Where's the real Cheng Yi?

93
00:07:54,060 --> 00:07:55,340
Want to know?

94
00:07:55,740 --> 00:07:56,780
Beg me.

95
00:07:57,420 --> 00:07:59,340
Maybe if you beg me, I'll tell you.

96
00:08:00,180 --> 00:08:01,980
I'll ask one more time.

97
00:08:02,500 --> 00:08:04,180
Where is Cheng Yi?

98
00:08:05,180 --> 00:08:06,460
Cheng Yi?

99
00:08:09,180 --> 00:08:10,580
Cheng Yi

100
00:08:11,940 --> 00:08:13,020
is dead.

101
00:08:15,500 --> 00:08:17,340
You killed him?

102
00:08:17,940 --> 00:08:18,700
I

103
00:08:21,220 --> 00:08:22,820
strangled him to death.

104
00:08:23,860 --> 00:08:26,300
I watched the Gu Nianchi in his eyes

105
00:08:26,700 --> 00:08:30,780
fade away little by little.

106
00:08:31,980 --> 00:08:34,460
And then I gave you
a brand new Cheng Yi.

107
00:08:34,860 --> 00:08:35,500
So?

108
00:08:36,180 --> 00:08:37,100
Satisfied now?

109
00:08:44,220 --> 00:08:48,910
♪How can broken love ever go on?♪

110
00:08:50,220 --> 00:08:55,540
♪How much hope must fade into despair?♪

111
00:08:56,040 --> 00:08:59,620
♪In the blink of an eye,
everything falls apart♪

112
00:08:59,960 --> 00:09:02,970
♪Bound by the fate we cannot escape♪

113
00:09:03,140 --> 00:09:08,260
♪You and I caught in
this tangled love and hate♪

114
00:09:09,380 --> 00:09:14,570
♪Fragile hearts can hardly bear goodbye♪

115
00:09:15,630 --> 00:09:21,230
♪How many times
must pain cut deep before we wake?♪

116
00:09:21,770 --> 00:09:25,150
♪I once gave myself
to you so completely♪

117
00:09:25,400 --> 00:09:28,349
♪Still holding on to that heart♪

118
00:09:28,350 --> 00:09:33,489
♪Only to suffer your fatal blow♪

119
00:09:33,490 --> 00:09:37,809
♪How desperately
I long to hold you close♪

120
00:09:37,810 --> 00:09:40,389
♪Yet I approach you with such caution♪

121
00:09:40,390 --> 00:09:42,669
♪How could a stand in ever have♪

122
00:09:42,670 --> 00:09:46,219
♪The right to be loved by you?♪

123
00:09:46,220 --> 00:09:50,749
♪If love is nothing
more than endless schemes♪

124
00:09:50,750 --> 00:09:53,280
♪Used and abandoned in the end♪

125
00:09:53,420 --> 00:09:55,369
♪Still I walk into♪

126
00:09:55,370 --> 00:09:58,969
♪The trap you set without regret♪

127
00:09:58,970 --> 00:10:03,019
♪How desperately
I long to hold you close♪

128
00:10:03,020 --> 00:10:05,599
♪Yet keep it buried deep inside♪

129
00:10:05,600 --> 00:10:07,759
♪A stand in can never cross♪

130
00:10:07,760 --> 00:10:11,199
♪The shortest distance between us♪

131
00:10:11,200 --> 00:10:16,170
♪If love can
make someone lose themselves♪

132
00:10:16,330 --> 00:10:21,000
♪Then let me stay by your side♪

133
00:10:23,780 --> 00:10:25,349
♪A substitute♪

134
00:10:25,350 --> 00:10:30,350
♪Needs no reason♪

